---
import Layout from './layout.astro'
import { getAssetPrefix } from '../../../../utils/path.js'
---

<Layout
  title="Breeding Philosophy"
  description="Dedicated to raising happy, healthy puppies in loving homes."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section
    class="position-relative text-light text-center"
    style={`background-image: url('${getAssetPrefix('/assets/img/breederspot-images/golden-retriever-1.jpg')}'); background-size: cover; background-position: center; height: 500px;`}
  >
    <!-- Overlay -->
    <div class="position-absolute top-0 start-0 w-100 h-100 bg-dark opacity-50"></div>
    <!-- Content -->
    <div
      class="position-relative d-flex flex-column justify-content-center align-items-center h-100 px-3"
    >
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-6 offset-lg-3">
          <h1 class="bg-primary-subtle text-primary d-inline-flex rounded-pill fs-5 px-4 py-2 mb-2">
            Our Breeding Philosophy
          </h1>
          <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold mb-3">Raising puppies the right way</h1>
          <p class="fs-4 mb-4">
            We believe that ethical breeding starts with love, continues with responsibility, and
            ends in a lifelong bond between dog and human. Our breeding practices are guided by
            transparency, veterinary excellence, and the emotional enrichment of every puppy.
          </p>
          <div class="d-flex justify-content-center flex-wrap gap-2 mb-2">
            <button class="btn btn-lg btn-primary rounded-pill px-4">
              View Puppies <i class="ri-arrow-right-line"></i>
            </button>
            <button class="btn btn-lg btn-outline-light rounded-pill px-4">
              <i class="ri-information-2-line"></i> Learn More
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Sets Us Apart -->
  <section class="bg-body py-5">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center mb-4">
        <h3 class="display-6 fw-bold mb-3">What sets us apart</h3>
        <p class="fs-5 mb-0">
          Our core values guide every step of the journey—from careful planning to joyful
          homecomings.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="row g-4">
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-3">
          <div class="card bg-primary-subtle card-lift rounded-5 h-100 p-4">
            <div class="card-body">
              <i class="ri-home-heart-fill text-primary fs-1"></i>
              <p class="fs-4 fw-semibold mb-2">Home-Like Spaces</p>
              <p class="fs-5 mb-2">
                Puppies are raised in warm, home-like settings—not cages—so they grow up confident
                and social.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-3">
          <div class="card bg-primary-subtle card-lift rounded-5 h-100 p-4">
            <div class="card-body">
              <i class="ri-shield-check-fill text-primary fs-1"></i>
              <p class="fs-4 fw-semibold mb-2">Health & Safety</p>
              <p class="fs-5 mb-2">
                Clean, climate-controlled environments maintained with veterinary-approved hygiene
                practices.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-3">
          <div class="card bg-primary-subtle card-lift rounded-5 h-100 p-4">
            <div class="card-body">
              <i class="ri-tree-fill text-primary fs-1"></i>
              <p class="fs-4 fw-semibold mb-2">Outdoor Play</p>
              <p class="fs-5 mb-2">
                Secure outdoor spaces where puppies can run, play, and develop motor skills through
                daily exercise.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-3">
          <div class="card bg-primary-subtle card-lift rounded-5 h-100 p-4">
            <div class="card-body">
              <i class="ri-user-heart-fill text-primary fs-1"></i>
              <p class="fs-4 fw-semibold mb-2">Socialization</p>
              <p class="fs-5 mb-2">
                Daily human interaction and sensory exposure help puppies become emotionally
                balanced and people-loving.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Puppy Development Protocol -->
  <section class="bg-body py-5">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center mb-4">
        <h3 class="display-6 fw-bold mb-3">Puppy Development Protocol</h3>
        <p class="fs-5 mb-0">
          A structured, loving approach to raise well-rounded puppies—nurtured week by week for
          optimal growth and socialization.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="row g-4">
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-3">
          <div class="card card-lift border rounded-5 h-100 p-4">
            <div class="card-body">
              <div class="display-6 fw-semibold text-primary mb-1">01.</div>
              <p class="fs-4 fw-semibold mb-2">Week 0–2</p>
              <p class="fs-5 mb-2">
                Puppies stay close to their mother, focusing on warmth, nursing, and bonding. We
                monitor health and begin gentle handling.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-3">
          <div class="card card-lift border rounded-5 h-100 p-4">
            <div class="card-body">
              <div class="display-6 fw-semibold text-primary mb-1">02.</div>
              <p class="fs-4 fw-semibold mb-2">Week 3–4</p>
              <p class="fs-5 mb-2">
                Eyes and ears open; puppies begin to walk. We introduce new textures to the puppies,
                gentle sounds, and human interaction daily.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-3">
          <div class="card card-lift border rounded-5 h-100 p-4">
            <div class="card-body">
              <div class="display-6 fw-semibold text-primary mb-1">03.</div>
              <p class="fs-4 fw-semibold mb-2">Week 5–8</p>
              <p class="fs-5 mb-2">
                Puppies explore more actively. We begin crate exposure, introduce solid food, and
                increase socialization with people.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-3">
          <div class="card card-lift border rounded-5 h-100 p-4">
            <div class="card-body">
              <div class="display-6 fw-semibold text-primary mb-1">04.</div>
              <p class="fs-4 fw-semibold mb-2">Week 9+</p>
              <p class="fs-5 mb-2">
                Puppies are ready to transition home. We offer support, resources, and guidance to
                families for continued development.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Comprehensive Health Testing Section -->
  <section class="bg-primary-subtle py-5">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row g-4">
        <!-- Text Column -->
        <div class="col-lg-8">
          <h3 class="display-6 fw-bold mb-3">Comprehensive Health Testing</h3>
          <p class="fs-5 mb-3">
            The health of our dogs is our top priority. Every parent dog undergoes thorough genetic
            screening, regular veterinary checkups, and OFA/CERF certifications where applicable. We
            ensure each puppy starts life with the strongest foundation—free from hereditary
            conditions and nurtured through responsible, science-backed care from day one.
          </p>
          <ul class="list-unstyled fs-5 mb-4">
            <li><i class="ri-check-line text-primary me-2"></i>Genetic Screening</li>
            <li>
              <i class="ri-check-line text-primary me-2"></i>Regular Veterinary Checkups
            </li>
            <li><i class="ri-check-line text-primary me-2"></i>OFA/CERF Certifications</li>
            <li><i class="ri-check-line text-primary me-2"></i>Deworming Protocols</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-lg btn-primary rounded-pill text-decoration-none px-4">
            Learn More<i class="ri-arrow-right-line ms-1"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
        <!-- Image Column -->
        <div class="col-lg-4 d-flex justify-content-center">
          <figure class="img-scale rounded-5">
            <img
              src={getAssetPrefix('/assets/img/breederspot-images/golden-retriever-2.jpg')}
              class="img-fluid"
              style="object-fit: cover;"
              alt="Golden Retriever"
            />
          </figure>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section
    class="text-light position-relative"
    style={`background-image: url('${getAssetPrefix('/assets/img/breederspot-images/gradient.jpg')}'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;`}
  >
    <div
      class="position-absolute top-0 start-0 w-100 h-100"
      style="background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);"
    >
    </div>
    <div class="container py-5 position-relative">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-8 offset-md-2">
          <h2 class="display-6 fw-bold mb-3">
            Find your perfect pup—<em>ethically, responsibly, and with love</em>.
          </h2>
          <p class="fs-5 mb-4">
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Dolorum quibusdam, libero
            corporis nemo!
          </p>
          <form class="row text-start g-3">
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <label for="fullName" class="form-label">Full Name</label>
              <input
                type="text"
                class="form-control form-control-lg"
                id="fullName"
                placeholder="Jane Doe"
                required
              />
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <label for="email" class="form-label">Email Address</label>
              <input
                type="email"
                class="form-control form-control-lg"
                id="email"
                placeholder="you@example.com"
                required
              />
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <label for="preferredBreed" class="form-label">Preferred Breed (optional)</label>
              <input
                type="text"
                class="form-control form-control-lg"
                id="preferredBreed"
                placeholder="e.g., Golden Retriever"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <label for="phone" class="form-label">Phone Number (optional)</label>
              <input
                type="tel"
                class="form-control form-control-lg"
                id="phone"
                placeholder="+1 (234) 567-8901"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-12">
              <label for="message" class="form-label">Tell us what you're looking for</label>
              <textarea
                class="form-control form-control-lg"
                id="message"
                rows="4"
                placeholder="Age, temperament, size, etc."></textarea>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 text-center">
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg rounded-pill px-4 mt-3">
                <i class="ri-sparkling-2-line me-1"></i> Find My Pup
              </button>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
